data.description: Located near the Monkey Junction, a 3 bedroom/2 bath home in the Archmill Place neighborhood. This home offers an open floorplan, laminate wood flooring and cathedral ceiling on the living room, a large owners suite, covered patio, shed, fenced in back yard and a one car garage. Updates to the home are HVAC in 2017, Hot water heater 2018 and a roof in 2019. The Front yard maintenance is included on the HOA. A short ride to shopping, dining and Carolina beach!
